title: Shop Kate Middleton's trending brown handbag as she makes surprise public appearance
text:
Kate Middleton made an unexpected public appearance while out shopping in London, and fans were quick to comment on the royal's stylish choice of handbag Kate Middleton stunned onlookers with a surprise appearance in London earlier this week, following her recent first solo engagement at the Royal Marsden Hospital. The Princess of Wales was spotted browsing for spectacles at Finlay's opticians in Notting Hill whilst chatting with staff members during her visit, with The Sun reporting the outing.
Meanwhile, celeb gossip Instagram account Deux Moi shared exclusive photos of Kate's outing, where one fashion-focused fan commented: "Cute little bag, wonder what brand it is. Nice to see her out and about after everything she's been through."
